    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;"><td style="padding: 12px;"><strong>LCP</strong> (Largest Contentful Paint)</td><td style="padding: 12px;">Loading speed – time until main content appears</td><td style="padding: 12px;">≤ 2.5 sec</td><td style="padding: 12px;">Critical – slow LCP = no voice result</td></tr>
      <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;"><td style="padding: 12px;"><strong>INP</strong> (Interaction to Next Paint)</td><td style="padding: 12px;">Responsiveness – how fast page reacts to taps</td><td style="padding: 12px;">≤ 200 ms</td><td style="padding: 12px;">High – voice users often tap after speaking</td></tr>
