  <p><strong>Investment:</strong> ~$50 (hosting upgrade) + 4 hours of work (in‑house). ROI positive within first week.</p>

  <h3>9. Mobile vs. Desktop: How Voice Search Behavior Differs in Kenya</h3>
  <p>Most voice searches happen on mobile, but some also occur on desktop (via Google Assistant on Windows or Mac) and smart speakers. However, the <strong>conversion path</strong> differs. A voice search on desktop often leads to a website visit on the same device. On mobile, it often leads to a call, a store visit, or a WhatsApp message.</p>
  <p>Therefore, your mobile optimization must prioritize <strong>click‑to‑call, WhatsApp click‑to‑chat, and Google Maps directions</strong>. Make these actions prominent and easy to find within the first scroll.</p>

