  <h2 style="border-left: 5px solid #f39c12; padding-left: 20px;">❓ FAQ Content Strategy: The #1 Voice Search Ranking Factor You Are Ignoring</h2>
  
  <p>If you take only one action from this entire guide, make it this: <strong>create a dedicated FAQ page and mark it up with FAQ schema.</strong> Why? Because Google voice assistants (Google Assistant, Siri, Alexa) pull answers directly from FAQ schema to answer voice queries. No other content format gives you a higher chance of being the spoken answer.</p>
  
  <p>A 2026 study by <strong>Backlinko (Kenya data chapter)</strong> analyzed 5,000 voice search results and found that <strong>63% of voice answers came from pages with FAQ schema</strong>. Pages without schema had less than 12% representation. The message is clear: <strong>If you are not using FAQ schema, you are invisible in voice search.</strong></p>

  <div style="background: #fff3e0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 16px; margin: 25px 0; border-left: 6px solid #f39c12;">
