  <h2 style="border-left: 5px solid #f39c12; padding-left: 20px;">🎯 Featured Snippets: The Direct Path to Google Voice Search Results</h2>
  
  <p>When you ask Google Assistant, “How much does SEO cost in Kenya?”, the voice that reads back an answer often comes from a <strong>featured snippet</strong> – the special box at the top of Google search results that highlights a direct answer. In fact, according to a 2026 study by <strong>Semrush (Kenya data chapter)</strong>, <strong>72% of voice search answers are pulled from featured snippets</strong>. If you want Google to read your content aloud, you must target and win featured snippets.</p>
  
