    <p>Google does not send a “voice” flag. But voice searches have distinct characteristics: they are longer, more conversational, often happen on mobile, and frequently lead to calls or “near me” actions. By combining Search Console filters, Google Business Profile insights, call tracking, and Analytics segments, you can isolate voice impact with 80‑90% confidence.</p>
