    <li>Set expectations for response time – voice users expect speed.</li>
  </ol>
  
  <p><strong>Voice search benefit:</strong> Google Assistant can say “You can message this business directly from their listing”. This reduces friction. Track message volume as a voice KPI.</p>

  <h3>5. Competitor GBP Analysis – Steal Their Voice Traffic</h3>
  <p>Your competitors’ GBP listings are public. Analyze them to find gaps and opportunities. For each main competitor, document:</p>
