  <h3>8. Managing Reviews for Voice Dominance</h3>
  <p>Voice assistants often read your average rating and the number of reviews. A business with 4.8 stars from 150 reviews will almost always be chosen over a business with 4.5 stars from 20 reviews, even if the second is closer.</p>
  
