  <h3>1. Voice Commerce Landscape in Kenya (2026 Data)</h3>
  <p>Understanding the current state of voice commerce helps you prioritize. Key statistics from the <strong>Kenya Voice Commerce Report 2026</strong> (compiled from Jumia, Safaricom, and Google data):</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Most purchased categories via voice:</strong> Groceries (41%), phone accessories (28%), household items (19%), fashion (12%).</li>
