  <h3>2. Data Source Integration – Where to Get Each KPI (Step by Step)</h3>
  <p>You will pull data from multiple free tools. Here is exactly where to find each number.</p>
  
  <h4>2.1 Google Search Console (GSC) – The Voice Query Goldmine</h4>
  <ul>
