    <li><strong>Featured snippets owned:</strong> GSC → Performance → Add filter “Search appearance” → “Featured snippet”. This shows all queries where your page appears in position zero. Record the count.</li>
    <li><strong>“Near me” impression volume:</strong> GSC → Performance → Add filter “Query” → “Query containing” → “near me”.</li>
    <li><strong>Average position (voice queries):</strong> Use the same query filters and look at the “Average position” column.</li>
  </ul>
