  <h4>2.2 Google Analytics (GA4) – Mobile Traffic & Call Clicks</h4>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Mobile organic traffic %:</strong> GA4 → Reports → Acquisition → Traffic acquisition → Add filter “Device category = mobile” → Compare organic sessions to total sessions.</li>
    <li><strong>Click‑to‑call rate:</strong> GA4 → Configure → Events → Look for “click_tel” (you must set this up as an event tag). If not set up, create a trigger for `click` on `a[href^="tel:"]`. Then create an exploration report showing unique users who clicked tel: links divided by total organic sessions.</li>
